headline: Alamo Group (ALG) Lags Q2 Earnings Estimates
summary: Alamo Group (ALG) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -4.46% and +4.07%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
